# Per-customer precompute subdirs (CUST-XXXX/) are large and
# regenerated by `./do precompute`. The two cross-tenant files
# (landing.json, help_related.json) ship via git so the deployed
# container has them without depending on the build pipeline
# running precompute. Glob-form is required: a directory-level
# `data/precomputed/` blanket-ignore would swallow the negations.
data/precomputed/*
!data/precomputed/landing.json
!data/precomputed/help_related.json
data/corporate_entities_raw.json
data/customers.json
data/employees.json
data/corporate_entities.json
data/help_articles.json
data/help_impressions.json
books/.out/

